<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你來得正好！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛剛<delay20 />
正在跟<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay8 />
討論野餐的話題呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不知道你們在說什麼野餐
還是遠足的，<delay20 />那很有趣嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在戶外吃便當，<delay20 />
真的很開心喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不然這樣好了，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我連大家的便當也一起做吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
你喜歡吃什麼樣的便當呢？</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別、<delay20 />別這樣啊！<delay frames="40" />
吃你親手做的便當<delay8 />也太讓人害臊了吧！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 10 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />是這樣嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<20_2 arg="0" /><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你喜歡吃什麼樣的便當呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">梅乾便當</message>
	<message label="005_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">飯糰便當</message>
	<message label="005_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">幕之內鐵路便當</message>
	<message label="005_d" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">海苔便當</message>
	<message label="005_e" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">卡通造型便當</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="2" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你這傢伙，<delay8 />吃得真是樸素啊！<delay frames="40" />
才這麼點東西，吃得飽嗎？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay frames="30" />
記得在我的便當裡<delay20 />
放一些玉子燒啊！<anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="2" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飯糰啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />啊，<delay frames="30" />
飯糰裡面的餡料，<delay20 />可以放玉子燒嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="2" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂喂，<delay20 />
你吃得可真好啊！<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />那裡面應該<delay20 />
會放玉子燒對吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="2" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />白飯上的海苔啊，<delay8 />
我老是切都切不斷，<delay20 />
所以我的便當就別加海苔啦。
<20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過拜託你，<delay20 />
幫我在旁邊放一些<delay8 />
玉子燒吧，<anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_0 arg="P0&gt;N1,N0&gt;N1" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那種幼稚的東西，<delay20 />
我可吃不下去啊！<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不過，<delay20 />
如果有放玉子燒的話，<delay8 />
管他什麼便當都無所謂啦，<anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
你會時常寫心意卡<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />寄回家嗎？</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我很少寫耶，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟也不知道<delay8 />
要寫什麼才好<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得你可以<delay8 />
寫一些自己的現況喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
那就<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「給老媽，<delay frames="30" />
現在<delay20 />我的鄰居，<delay20 />
正在教我怎麼寫信。」<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay20 />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />我覺得可以呀。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接著寫下去吧！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼接著寫？<delay8 />
剛剛那樣就寫完啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼這樣～<delay frames="40" />
這樣<delay8 />感覺不就像是
我教得很差嗎～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />才不會咧！<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我身邊有
願意教我寫信的朋友！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />這樣<delay8 />我老媽就知道<delay8 />
我過得很好啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你能用稍微委婉一點的方式講話，<delay20 />
給別人的印象應該會變好喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼啊？<delay frames="30" />
我講話已經很委婉了啊！<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底還想要我怎樣啦？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒辦法再<tag a="110" b="0" />委婉一點了嗎？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />既然這樣，<delay20 />就稍微改變一下
說話方式如何呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道了，<delay frames="40" />
那不然<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的那句「<tag a="110" b="5" />」，<delay8 />
也讓我用用吧。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣聽起來，<delay8 />應該多少會
有點變化吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Aha" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和平常不一樣，感覺好新鮮喔！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />果然只要改變說話方式，<delay8 />
給人的印象也會有變化呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>